paraphrases: Can I take the 492 course next term ?
Is the 492 course available next term ?
sql: SELECT COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SECTION_NUMBER , SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER , SEMESTERalias0.YEAR FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 , SEMESTER AS SEMESTERalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID AND COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 492 AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER = "FA" AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SEMESTER AND SEMESTERalias0.YEAR = 2016 ;
